---
title: Miso Apricot Chicken with Ginger Cauliflower Rice & Zesty Green Beans
description: No need to be chicken about making this delicious, saucy meal. Crispy chicken cutlets are drizzled with an umami-packed sauce of apricot jam, miso broth, lime juice, and butter. On the side, there’s fluffy, aromatic ginger rice, plus roasted carrots tossed with lime zest. Talk about a weeknight dinner worth hatching out!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/668d3e0c32f1db5f2525c6b7-1d227547.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/66d8a25384d92a4240f34cf1-en-US.pdf
cuisine: Asian
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
